{"tid":1612591,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"港警槍擊高中生 《紐時》影片完整還原始末曝4大關鍵","createTime":"2019-10-02T09:51:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-02T23:42:26.000Z","uid":35790,"like":36,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"dfd331ec4c3518bb94292a405daa66d02350204d","tid":1612591,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T09:51:48.000Z","msg":"港警槍擊高中生 《紐時》影片完整還原始末曝4大關鍵<br />\n<br />\n2019-10-02<br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕香港反送中運動持續延燒，昨（1日）驚傳港警近距離開槍射擊1名高中生，實彈打中左胸，由於此為反送中運動爆發以來首次出現民眾中彈事件，引發各界譁然，港警聲稱開槍「合情合法」，有外媒透過不同角度的影片，交叉比對分析，釐清前因後果，同時也暴露港警許多違反聯合國規範行為。<br />\n<br />\n《紐約時報》透過不同角度的影片，將槍擊事件全貌完整揭露。昨日中國國慶，香港街頭當天再現抗議人潮，荃灣附近爆發警民衝突，1名落單港警遭到抗議人士追打，港警倒地後眾人一擁而上圍毆，抗議人士揮舞手中的鐵棍、槌子、板手等武器，接著另1名港警衝上來，手中左輪手槍已上膛，直接近距離射擊。<br />\n<br />\n槍聲響起抗議群眾鳥獸散，而18歲高中生中彈倒地，倒地後另1名抗議人士企圖過來幫助中彈高中生，卻被港警打倒在地，遠方有人丟擲燃燒瓶，其他警力過來支援現場，至少有2人拔槍，1人手持胡椒噴霧。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">影片揭露開第一槍的員警手中有持有橡皮彈手槍、腰間繫有胡椒噴霧等非致命武器，然而中彈者卻被擱置在地，無人提供急救。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n《紐約時報》表示，根據聯合國規範警方用槍時機只有在面臨死亡或重傷的威脅下，同時開槍前必須示警（如對空鳴槍），可是從影片中可以看到開槍港警似乎沒有做出警告就直接射擊，《紐時》認為這此事件標示著警方執法明顯升級，未來抗議活動恐越演越烈。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">醫師作家蔡依橙也從《紐時》影片中歸納出4個重點，「武勇示威者湧向警察，武器有鐵棍、槌子、板手」、「警察被推倒地，並被圍毆，然後附近的警察直接拔槍，即使手上有鎮暴槍等非致命性武器以及辣椒噴霧可用」、「警察沒有對空鳴槍示警，而是直接開槍，而且針對致命區域」、「示威者中槍倒地後，沒有提供緊急救助，而是持續壓制」</span></span>，稱《紐時》果然專業，利用各種不同角度影片還原事件前因後果。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com/amp/s/news.ltn.com.tw/amp/news/world/breakingnews/2933794\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Famp%2Fs%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Famp%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2933794&d=zBKsoIV%2FeLhWSsP5H2J%2Bms0oCCb%2BFWW1Qd8KXu5iEc8%3D&h=f1e2cc39\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com/amp/s/news.ltn.com.tw/amp/news/world/breakingnews/2933794</a>"},{"pid":"dd3a8bccb4f5b3b9c80aa2d03eff3c7641e394a9","tid":1612591,"uid":35790,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T09:53:14.000Z","msg":"蔡依橙的閱讀筆記<br />\n6 小時前<br />\n紐約時報果然專業！取得各種不同角度的港警槍擊示威者影片後，交叉比對分析，然後說明前因後果。<br />\n　<br />\n1. 武勇示威者湧向警察，武器有鐵棍、槌子、板手。<br />\n　<br />\n2. 警察被推倒地，並被圍毆，然後附近的警察直接拔槍，即使手上有鎮暴槍等非致命性武器以及辣椒噴霧可用。<br />\n　<br />\n3. 警察沒有對空鳴槍示警，而是直接開槍，而且針對致命區域。<br />\n　<br />\n4. 示威者中槍倒地後，沒有提供緊急救助，而是持續壓制。<br />\n　<br />\n所違反的聯合國規範，也在片中清楚說明。<br />\n<img src=\"https://external.fhkg10-1.fna.fbcdn.net/safe_image.php?d=AQAFpA-o5VYMQBS-&amp;w=476&amp;h=249&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic01.nyt.com%2Fimages%2F2019%2F10%2F01%2Fworld%2Fasia%2FYT_STILL__onsite_v1%2FYT_STILL__onsite_v1-videoSixteenByNine1050.jpg&amp;cfs=1&amp;upscale=1&amp;fallback=news_d_placeholder_publisher&amp;_nc_hash=AQB_pQAtkhbe1SRW\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fexternal.fhkg10-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fsafe_image.php%3Fd%3DAQAFpA-o5VYMQBS-%26w%3D476%26h%3D249%26url%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fstatic01.nyt.com%252Fimages%252F2019%252F10%252F01%252Fworld%252Fasia%252FYT_STILL__onsite_v1%252FYT_STILL__onsite_v1-videoSixteenByNine1050.jpg%26cfs%3D1%26upscale%3D1%26fallback%3Dnews_d_placeholder_publisher%26_nc_hash%3DAQB_pQAtkhbe1SRW&h=8e5150c3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"230ed480867aedd7abcff865ee70261dd41118ed","tid":1612591,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T10:08:27.000Z","msg":"721   811   831   101"},{"pid":"ad9a1e19509f3e8548faada6771dcc5b74fed61b","tid":1612591,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T10:13:33.000Z","msg":"《紐時》影片完整還原始末曝4大關鍵<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.nytimes.com/video/world/asia/100000006745719/hong-kong-protester-shot.html?smid=fb-share&amp;fbclid=IwAR1afpIUz-fLTVf4PyUYurXDg5yitI50fG6C0mEdRcH6onWWBoTdB-UBgdw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2Fvideo%2Fworld%2Fasia%2F100000006745719%2Fhong-kong-protester-shot.html%3Fsmid%3Dfb-share%26fbclid%3DIwAR1afpIUz-fLTVf4PyUYurXDg5yitI50fG6C0mEdRcH6onWWBoTdB-UBgdw&d=zBKsoIV%2FeLhWSsP5H2J%2Bms0oCCb%2BFWW1Qd8KXu5iEc8%3D&h=67076819\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.nytimes.com/video/world/asia/100000006745719/hong-kong-protester-shot.html?smid=fb-share&amp;fbclid=IwAR1afpIUz-fLTVf4PyUYurXDg5yitI50fG6C0mEdRcH6onWWBoTdB-UBgdw</a>"},{"pid":"f2b6aab15f4f5cccd33b49da88c85c353cc4dd0d","tid":1612591,"uid":121146,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T10:15:08.000Z","msg":"以後對啲狗往死裏打  乜都唔撚洗講"},{"pid":"cb576c1bd444a9f11bad8679efa97ce11da43132","tid":1612591,"uid":236646,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T10:19:22.000Z","msg":"完全係想殺人，林鄭講對話就係開實彈殺人。對你老母"},{"pid":"fd60e37dd198beb5c2f32df0d2ba715d80e1689e","tid":1612591,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f2b6aab15f4f5cccd33b49da88c85c353cc4dd0d","tid":1612591,"uid":121146,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T10:15:08.000Z","msg":"以後對啲狗往死裏打  乜都唔撚洗講"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T10:19:30.000Z","msg":"今日聽燒山講<br />\n話9個套裝備<br />\n用棍點打都唔會受傷"},{"pid":"dd38f54dc88c832600a116d2c07d636e5778653f","tid":1612591,"uid":20658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T10:19:41.000Z","msg":"有心射架啦死黑警"},{"pid":"98c20b5c5587afbf99eb80d26a55395b9b2f3dd4","tid":1612591,"uid":121146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fd60e37dd198beb5c2f32df0d2ba715d80e1689e","tid":1612591,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f2b6aab15f4f5cccd33b49da88c85c353cc4dd0d","tid":1612591,"uid":121146,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T10:15:08.000Z","msg":"以後對啲狗往死裏打  乜都唔撚洗講"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T10:19:30.000Z","msg":"今日聽燒山講<br />\n話9個套裝備<br />\n用棍點打都唔會受傷"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T10:23:32.000Z","msg":"打頸  捉手  打關節"},{"pid":"53942477106dd1e20660bdc252db3e4e670bba18","tid":1612591,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"98c20b5c5587afbf99eb80d26a55395b9b2f3dd4","tid":1612591,"uid":121146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fd60e37dd198beb5c2f32df0d2ba715d80e1689e","tid":1612591,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f2b6aab15f4f5cccd33b49da88c85c353cc4dd0d","tid":1612591,"uid":121146,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T10:15:08.000Z","msg":"以後對啲狗往死裏打  乜都唔撚洗講"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T10:19:30.000Z","msg":"今日聽燒山講<br />\n話9個套裝備<br />\n用棍點打都唔會受傷"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T10:23:32.000Z","msg":"打頸  捉手  打關節"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T10:26:58.000Z","msg":"佢對脚有護膝護脛"},{"pid":"c56e58ff80e42dfea15041aeb9f7db960e2500b9","tid":1612591,"uid":100205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T10:30:25.000Z","msg":"731 831 101"},{"pid":"1754160e4027e29decebc79c867d29fadf36bb3e","tid":1612591,"uid":35790,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T10:32:48.000Z","msg":"【黑色10.1】張崑陽去信歐美澳洲政要揭魔警暴行：讓自由世界孤立香港警察<br />\n<br />\n昨日「十一國殤」警察大規模拘捕，黃大仙一名中五男生遭到警員以實彈射中左胸，今午民間記者會就事件批評警方的暴力行為，嚴重危害學生的生命，以恐怖份子的行徑威嚇市民，如同失去人性。香港大專學界國際事務代表團發言人張崑陽亦有出席今午記者會，他指經歷過昨日學生被開槍射擊，代表團已立即「運用咗過去一個月因外訪而所累積的人脈」，將學生被開槍的相關消息發信給他們，並已連繫了澳洲、英國、德國的議員，以及美國參眾兩院、歐盟歐洲議會和聯合國人權事務高級專員辦事處等，並將此新聞公開給全世界的政要，希望他們能夠監察香港警察的「惡行」。<br />\n<br />\n曾於上月到美國國會發言的張崑陽補充，美國國會屬下的國會及行政當局中國委員會（CECC）已發出聲明回應事件，要求政府立即成立獨立調查委員會，調查警方暴行和平息社會紛爭。張崑陽承諾，代表團會將香港警察的暴行公諸於世，「自由世界同香港警察割蓆」，強調「自由世界將會站在勇敢嘅香港人和中學生」，呼籲每個國家都制定《全球馬格尼茨基人權問責法》（The Global Magnitsky Act），制裁嚴重違反人權公約的香港警察，永久禁止進入「自由世界」，「生生世世咁係大灣區生活，共享所謂嘅中國繁榮，做中國的奴才」。張昆陽最後亦呼籲，美國國會盡快通過《香港人權與民主法案》，並禁止售賣武器給香港警察，達到「進一步的孤立」，及將香港問題國際化。<br />\n&lt;蘋果&gt;"},{"pid":"53d04c9ffcbc58f0abf6eaa6749c7d51ae99b945","tid":1612591,"uid":249979,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T10:36:39.000Z","msg":"黑警跳過法庭裁判，凌駕基本法、人道法<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">擅自對在場示威者判以槍殺死刑</span></span><br />\n香港警察正式向全世界民主法治國家宣戰"},{"pid":"2f832c3fee271c1e47d4507d8b9df1dad791a808","tid":1612591,"uid":127704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T10:39:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"de3